## Migraciones

```
0051_add_series_columns_to_assistant_events
  series_id            bigint nullable FK → assistant_events(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
  occurrence_at        timestamp nullable   — slot RRULE que representa esta fila
  reminders_template_json json nullable     — solo en masters; offsets para MaterializeSeriesWindow
  INDEX(series_id)

0052_add_referenceable_to_assistant_events
  referenceable_type   string nullable
  referenceable_id     string nullable
  INDEX(referenceable_type, referenceable_id)
```

`reminders_template_json` formato:
```json
[{ "offset": "-7 days", "message": "En una semana es X" }, ...]
```

